column5: A while back a board member ordered  bunch of buck tails from me (15), only thing was that he wanted longshank. Since I couldn't find any online I tried to hire someone to pour them for me, it has been over a month and they still aren't ready so I'm looking for other options. If anyone is interested I need jigs (any style i can tie on, preferred minnow head) in sizes 1/8, 1/4, and 3/8 oz, I need them by next week, pm me for details.  Thanks, Christopher
Talk to bigugly he does and he also makes sinkers too!
Chris pm me with the the type of hook and size, and the type of head and weight you want.
Just want to get gaspumper's attention. Please respond to my PM's
anyone know the price of lead.. ? i found a bunch of lead pucks and big chunks of left overs from making torpedo's for lake ontario.
